divs: Sighting Detailswe had this experience few months back, but i didnt think any one is going to believe us. until i saw your progarm on THE HISTORY , thats how i thought i could share it with the world. i and two of my friends went on a picnic to a mountainous region near the quetta city at about 4 hours ride. as we were going to leave that place one of my friend ahmad noticed something in the sky and he started yelling, and showed us that (ufo) thing in the sky, there were 4 small but bright lights in circle, in the begining when we saw it it was still but then it started moving about 5 min later, it was really amazing i mean no one of us could believe what we were watching, coz we had never seen anything like that before. we were in sight of that object for about 25 min and then it disappeared into tne sky. for about a week we were trying to convince family and others about what we have seen but no one believed us. we also took some photographs of it, but doesnt describe it very well.
Summary: many small lights glowing in a circle, like a disc is flying.
